(155,1,"2018-03-05 09:19:32","2018-03-05 09:19:32","<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Quick To Follow Up Calls</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kneen Electrical Services are polite and friendly to both ourselves, landlords</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">and tenants. They are quick to act and follow up our calls on the same day.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">They advise landlords of best options available and give a free quote if required.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kneen Electrical Services form part of our maintenance team.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dawson’s and their landlords value their excellent service.</p>","Richard Wood","","publish","closed","closed","","quick-to-follow-up-calls","","","2018-03-05 09:58:48","2018-03-05 09:58:48","",0,"http://kneenelectricalservices.local/?post_type=testimonial-free&#038;p=155",0,"testimonial-free","",0),
(156,1,"2018-03-05 09:19:58","2018-03-05 09:19:58","<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Open, honest and friendly</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fantastic service! He came I have used Kneen Electrical Services for work both at home, and my church.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I have found them to be professional, neat and tidy, and friendly in their dealings with myself and other church staff. Their prices are very reasonable, and as a committed Christian I know they value honesty and openness in their business.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I have no hesitation in recommending them.</p>","Tony Kershaw","","publish","closed","closed","","open-honest-and-friendly","","","2018-03-05 09:57:21","2018-03-05 09:57:21","",0,"http://kneenelectricalservices.local/?post_type=testimonial-free&#038;p=156",0,"testimonial-free","",0),
(157,1,"2018-03-05 09:20:25","2018-03-05 09:20:25","<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">DBS checked</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kneen Electrical Services come into school regularly to do ad hoc</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">electrical repairs sometimes at very short notice and larger electrical projects.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">They also are responsible for the ongoing electrical testing which is</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">required for insurance purposes. Chris Kneen is DBS checked so</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">can be on site anytime</p>","Governors","","publish","closed","closed","","dbs-checked","","","2018-03-05 09:58:17","2018-03-05 09:58:17","",0,"http://kneenelectricalservices.local/?post_type=testimonial-free&#038;p=157",0,"testimonial-free","",0),
(158,1,"2018-03-05 09:20:53","2018-03-05 09:20:53","<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Responds to Emergency Calls and Always Helps</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I have known Chris for several years and he has done quite a few jobs</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">for me, some of which were major ones. I have found him to be trustworthy</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">and dependable. More importantly he responds to emergency calls and</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">always helps. He is honest and reliable, and I do not hesitate to recommend</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">him to anyone seeking an electrician</p>","Bob Foulkes","","publish","closed","closed","","responds-to-emergency-calls-and-always-helps","","","2018-03-05 09:57:42","2018-03-05 09:57:42","",0,"http://kneenelectricalservices.local/?post_type=testimonial-free&#038;p=158",0,"testimonial-free","",0),
